ies at the heart of policy solutions.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Mrz 2024) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Ethnic Studies / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2024z978311129965540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781529221732423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781529221732/original  a978-3-11-129965-5  Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2024b2024  aGBV-deGruyter-alles